  <heading>PUNPKHI, PUNPKLO</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>
      <para>Unpack and widen half of predicate</para>
    </brief>
    <authored>
      <para>This instruction unpacks elements from the lowest or highest half of the source
predicate and places them in elements of twice their
size within the destination predicate.  This instruction is unpredicated.</para>
    </authored>
    <predicated>False</predicated>
  </desc>
